# Frontend Rule

- Keep API calls and contracts centralized in canonical API/type modules.
- Extract non-trivial UI logic into focused custom hooks.
- Preserve strict TypeScript and avoid `any`.
- Optimize rendering for chat-scale streaming updates and long message lists.
- Run `lint`, `typecheck`, and relevant tests for changed frontend behavior.
